metadata.name: Organica Osmotrophica
metadata.description:
Organica Osmotrophica

Imagine a world beyond our own, where thoughts and ideas take on a life of their own. Where the boundless power of our imagination brings our wildest dreams to reality. Where our ideas take shape and form, given the freedom they deserve to flourish. These microcosms would be accessible to all of us, allowing us to truly explore the other being. This is the realm of the mind, where the impossible becomes possible and the conceptual evolves into the tangible. Let us embrace this boundless potential and bring our greatest visions to life.

Holders will enter a raffle for a 3D animated 1/1 to be released within the next 3 months.

Please hold for the love of art.

Created in Houdini 2560x1080 25fps  
Sound by Onyro.
